  "detailed_description": "The Perplexing Orb returns in a brand new entry packed with new features! New art style, new levels, and new game play mechanics!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/8d23b2abcfaf166c7b43c4f3a5db9426.poster.avif?t=1756236664\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/8d23b2abcfaf166c7b43c4f3a5db9426.webm?t=1756236664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/8d23b2abcfaf166c7b43c4f3a5db9426.mp4?t=1756236664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In this third entry to The Perplexing Orb franchise, you have the ability to bounce your way through all new challenges!<br><br>The game contains <strong>40 all new story stages</strong> all designed around distance, height, and the ability to jump!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/920b9613e705a7fdf947800ce1147204.poster.avif?t=1756236664\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/920b9613e705a7fdf947800ce1147204.webm?t=1756236664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/920b9613e705a7fdf947800ce1147204.mp4?t=1756236664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game features an all new retro inspired art style with different graphical options. You can either play the game in crisp full HD or with a pixel filter to make the low poly art match closer to the PS1 era aesthetic! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/9d527c5080874415d73dd93bc1e43737.avif?t=1756236664\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br><strong>INSANE Challenge Mode Levels</strong> make a return in this entry! Once you conquer the main story stages, brace yourself for 8 incredibly difficult stages to test your resolve!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/25f8e42e971127c4968b68487f6f896f.poster.avif?t=1756236664\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/25f8e42e971127c4968b68487f6f896f.webm?t=1756236664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/25f8e42e971127c4968b68487f6f896f.mp4?t=1756236664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Stage Designs are filled with all sorts of new obstacles and tools like cracking ice, elevators, moving platforms and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/ffe4b83e20930d4d70f6a64c493e221a.poster.avif?t=1756236664\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/ffe4b83e20930d4d70f6a64c493e221a.webm?t=1756236664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/ffe4b83e20930d4d70f6a64c493e221a.mp4?t=1756236664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>ALL NEW TIME TRIAL MODE.</strong><br>Race for gold medal times OR test yourself against incredibly difficult dev times in the brand new time trial mode!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/d264b7d1c3bbdfbdb68cd023c3e66c61.poster.avif?t=1756236664\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/d264b7d1c3bbdfbdb68cd023c3e66c61.webm?t=1756236664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/d264b7d1c3bbdfbdb68cd023c3e66c61.mp4?t=1756236664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
